{
 "name": "RPlog_Out_of_the_Frying_Pan",
 "title": "Out of the Frying Pan",
 "summary": "After a rancor scatters their forest camp at daybreak, a column of New Republic marines under the Twi'lek scout Lieutenant Wrista crosses a grassy plain toward a downed X-Wing and its huddled pilot, Lance 'Wildman.' Wrista hands command of the march to the concussed but capable Leyanne as a test, then ranges off to scout. The marines encounter a herd of towering Malkloc plainstalkers, and Leyanne, keeping the trigger-happy Corporal Kayl'bre and the steady Kaylen in check, correctly reads the giant herbivores as non-threatening, letting the territorial family move off without a fight. Reuniting with the wry Wrista and recovering Lance at the wreck, Leyanne tends the pilot's wounds and earns her commander's praise for cool-headed judgment under pressure.",
